\par\pard\plain \sa200\sl276\slmult1\ql\ltrch\loch \f1\fs22\b1\i0
\par\plain {\f0\fs22\b0\i0 The cancelling of the MRS programme has had a notable impact on national-level facilities. Indeed, we have observed a policy movement toward only fundamental international facilities (admittedly with some exceptions).Nonetheless, researchers are especially cognizant that the view a facility is \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93National level\u8221\'94\u8221\'94 is now a derogatory term in the eyes of many at the funding councils.}
